{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Anathema's Symphony</strong> is a top-down rhythm-shooter that forces you to move, shoot, and dodge to the beat. It combines rhythm-based combat with modern 3D graphics and a world full of lore waiting to be explored.<br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292500/extras/video_1.1.gif?t=1731680901\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022\t<strong>Rhythm-Driven Combat:</strong> In Anathema's Symphony, every action is tied to the beat. Both the enemy and player attacks are synched to the rhythm, which often times changes, for more unpredictability and a greater challenge! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022\t<strong>Vertical Complexity Mechanics:</strong> As you progress, Anathema's Symphony ramps up the challenge\u2014not by offering upgrades for your character, but by demanding tighter timings and better movement. Each level is tuned to be a greater challenge than the last.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022\t<strong>Genre-Bending Experience:</strong> Blending the top down dodging with  rhythm driven combat offers a largely unexplored take on the genre that will for sure freshen up your experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292500/extras/video_2.gif?t=1731680901\" />  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to enter a world where rhythm and skill rule. With unique 3D visuals, challenging mechanics, and a musical flow that controls everything, Anathema's Symphony offers a rhythm-shooter experience unlike any other. Are you ready?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731680901","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292500/page.bg.jpg?t=1731680901","capsu